"http://www.plum.com/learnmore.html", "title": "Plum - Collect, share, and connect your world", "tags": "web2.0 sns share ", "name": "mobo", "posttime": "2006-02-08 14:38:51", "ip": "202.196.64.100", "mark": 1, "note": "First you google, then you Plum... \r\nCollect and share what matters\r\nPlum lets you put all the stuff you care about, stumble across or need in one place. Collect and save from the web, your email, or your computer. Then personalize and share it with others (if you like). You can even discover other collections like yours and collect them too.", "imagename": "fbadc5b5-566d-4992-a782-a90eb4135fe2.gif", "infoid": 748, "category": "technology_web2", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["web2.0", "sns", "share"]}, {"url": "http://net.sitesled.com/2006/02/top-10-websites-you-should-know-about.html", "title": "top 10 websites you should know about", "tags": "web2.0 ", "name": "kukusky", "posttime": "2006-02-08 13:42:11", "ip": "218.83.218.204", "mark": 2, "note": "Recently a ton of great sites have popped up on the internet. Many of them you may not have heard of, that is the main point of this post. I've decided not to list popular well known sites such as flickr and others (although it could be disputed what is well known and what isn't). Without further ado here are the top 10 sites you should know about:", "imagename": "", "infoid": 747, "category": "technology_web2", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["web2.0"]}, {"url": "http://www.pconline.com.cn/pcedu/soft/wl/assist/0602/754633.html", "title": "\u8ba9Gmail\u6210\u4e3a\u65e0\u9650\u4e0a\u4f20\u7684\u7f51\u7edc\u786c\u76d8", "tags": "gmail gmaildriver \u786c\u76d8 \u4e0a\u4f20 \u65e0\u9650 ", "name": "yee", "posttime": "2006-02-08 12:20:04", "ip": "218.85.162.61", "mark": 3, "note": "GMailstore\u7a81\u7834\u4e86GMail\u7684\u9644\u4ef610M\u5927\u5c0f\u9650\u5236,\u53ef\u4ee5\u4f20\u8f93\u4efb\u610f\u5927\u5c0f\u6587\u4ef6\uff0c\u800cGMailDriver\u81f3\u4eca\u6700\u65b0\u7248\u672c\u5219\u4ecd\u53d7\u6b64\u9650\u5236\u3002\u800c\u4e14\u662f\u5168\u4e2d\u6587\u8f6f\u4ef6\uff0c\u7531\u56fd\u4eba\u5f00\u53d1\uff0c\u4e0d\u5b58\u5728\u4e2d\u6587\u6587\u4ef6\u540d\u51fa\u73b0\u4e71\u7801\u95ee\u9898!", "imagename": "85ef348e-76a0-490c-80fa-613dad8a60c2.jpg", "infoid": 746, "category": "technology_google", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["gmail", "\u786c\u76d8", "\u4e0a\u4f20", "\u65e0\u9650"]}, {"url": "http://www.gamerandy.com/archives/2006/02/ps3_skuered_1.shtml", "title": "PS3\u5c06\u6709\u4e24\u4e2aSKU, \u4ef7\u683c\u4e3a$399\u548c$599", "tags": "PS3 Sony SKU game ", "name": "jette", "posttime": "2006-02-08 09:36:22", "ip": "218.75.124.66", "mark": 2, "note": "The rumor comes from an EBgames employee who says that EB and GS will start taking preorders for the PS3 soon. They will be offering to different versions to preorder.", "imagename": "", "infoid": 745, "category": "technology_games", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["ps3", "sony", "sku", "game"]}, {"url": "http://www.apple.com/ipodnano/", "title": "Apple Lunched 1GB iPod Nano", "tags": "Apple iPod 1GB Nano ", "name": "jette", "posttime": "2006-02-08 09:32:05", "ip": "218.75.124.66", "mark": 5, "note": "Take everything you love about iPod and shrink it. Now shrink it again. With 1GB (240 songs), 2GB (500 songs) and 4GB (1,000 songs) models starting at $149, the pencil-thin iPod nano packs the entire iPod experience into an impossibly small design. So small, it will take your music places you never dreamed of.", "imagename": "4f5716d4-5b11-4de9-832c-d2a32a6b66fe.jpg", "infoid": 744, "category": "technology_apple", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["apple", "ipod", "1gb", "nano"]}, {"url": "http://www.googlevideodownload.com/", "title": "\u4e0b\u8f7dGoogle Video\uff0c\u6709AVI, MP4, FLV\u683c\u5f0f", "tags": "Google Video \u4e0b\u8f7d ", "name": "mobo", "posttime": "2006-02-08 05:27:26", "ip": "202.196.64.100", "mark": 7, "note": "\u6709\u4e9bvideo google\u5bf9\u6211\u4eec\u662f\u4e0d\u5f00\u653e\u7684\uff0c\u901a\u8fc7\u8fd9\u4e2a\u7f51\u7ad9\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u641e\u5b9a\u4e86\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u8fd8\u53ef\u4ee5\u4e0b\u8f7d\u4fdd\u5b58\u4e3aAVI\uff0cMP4\u683c\u5f0f\u5f71\u7247\u4ee5\u53ca\u63d0\u4f9b\u6700\u4e00\u4e9b\u70ed\u95e8\u89c6\u9891\u6392\u884c\u3002", "imagename": "18b287e3-f382-40b4-8708-db1a6e6d9b6c", "infoid": 743, "category": "technology_Google", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["google", "video", "\u4e0b\u8f7d"]}, {"url": "http://www.universaldisplay.com/", "title": "\u8f6f\u53ef\u53d8\u5f62\u7684OLED\u663e\u793a\u5c4f", "tags": "Flexible OLED display ", "name": "mobo", "posttime": "2006-02-08 05:09:36", "ip": "202.196.64.100", "mark": 3, "note": "Universal Display Corporation is a leading organic light emitting device (OLED) technology developer with a broad intellectual property portfolio, years of experience in OLED research and development, and entrepreneurial management expertise.  Our proprietary technologies and materials can provide OLED manufacturers and product developers with product differentiation and a competitive advantage. Phosphorescent, flexible, transparent and top emission OLEDs, to name a few, are important examples of Universal Display Corporation's core OLED technologies.", "imagename": "06d423ba-49f7-4f46-bbee-2785cd8bd9ef.gif", "infoid": 742, "category": "technology_gadgets", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["flexible", "oled", "display"]}, {"url": "http://www.sketchswap.com/", "title": "Sketch Swap : \u6709\u8da3\u7684\u